title: Admin Console - Netskope Knowledge Portal
content: The Netskope Admin console, or tenant , provides the ability to use all the Netskope products and services in one location. Starting with administrative functions, like tenant access and privileges, to viewing informative dashboards, managing incidents, using Skope IT to monitor activity, assess app risk and advanced analytics, and create reports.
